body_html:
@pkulzc By running toco to get tflite flatbuffer format file, I got the following error:

F tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco/tooling_util.cc:1589] Array FeatureExtractor/MobilenetV1/MobilenetV1/Conv2d_0/Relu6, which is an input to the DepthwiseConv operator producing the output array FeatureExtractor/MobilenetV1/MobilenetV1/Conv2d_1_depthwise/Relu6, is lacking min/max data, which is necessary for quantization. Either target a non-quantized output format, or change the input graph to contain min/max information, or pass --default_ranges_min= and --default_ranges_max= if you do not care about the accuracy of results.
Aborted (core dumped)

Any idea..?
